metadata.description: Sneakerheads, it's time to add some serious heat to your collection! The Genesis Collection brings you new-age superhero NFTs that blend sneaker culture and comic book art into one epic drop. With each one being a one-of-a-kind digital collectible stored on the Ethereum blockchain, you know you're getting the real deal. Don't miss out on this chance to cop some fresh, exclusive superhero style and take your collection to the next level.
metadata.name: Zneaker Headz #1
